# Cloudflare Workers static-assets headers.
#
# GO-LIVE: the X-Robots-Tag below is the ONE indexability control the INDEXABLE
# build flag cannot reach (a static Cloudflare config file — see src/lib/seo.ts
# and docs/GO-LIVE.md). It is left noindex on purpose: if go-live forgets it the
# site simply stays out of the index (a safe failure) instead of accidentally
# indexing the clone. Step 1 of the go-live checklist is to DELETE the
# X-Robots-Tag line below.
/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive
